Short Description: Stop suffering every time you put on your shoes thanks to the extendable metal shoe horn! It's the simplest, quickest and most comfortable way to put on some shoes without effort and you won't need to bend down. Metal shoe horn (Approx. 3.5 x 32 x 1.5 cm). Extendable (from 32 up to 80 cm). With rubber grip. Perfect for the elderly or people with mobility problems. Free point-of-sale display when buying 25 units.
